    "Some had also experimented with using it to streamline their own teaching workflows.",
    "However, uses were largely exploratory and geared around improving student and instructor AI literacy levels: there is still significant progress to make in establishing how generative AI can be used responsibly and effectively in specific courses and disciplines in the longer term.",
    "13 In order to help users think more critically about the best uses for generative AI, it will first be necessary to continue raising individuals' levels of familiarity with the technology.",
    "Skeptics with low adoption levels also tended to have low levels of familiarity.",
    "Overall, interviewees in our variable degrees of specificity about their discipline."
